    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras/b14ab9e0e4382df9415d543c0b07ed79.avif?t=1771494782\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras_big/b14ab9e0e4382df9415d543c0b07ed79.avif?t=1771494782 width=800 height=91 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《拉米：程式與咖啡》</strong>- 是一款融合日系风格、经营模拟与节奏玩法的3D休闲游戏。故事围绕着一位厌倦现状的年轻主角，在收到爷爷的一封信后，决定辞去工作并继承爷爷留下的咖啡厅。然而，主角在咖啡厅楼上发现了一间隐藏的研究室，并意外地唤醒了AI机器人少女——拉米。这一发现揭开了爷爷生前的秘密，原来他正是拉米的开发者。从此，主角与拉米携手经营这家充满怀旧与科技感的咖啡厅，共同展开一段奇妙的生活旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras/e95ec2dfd6c5a253c6bf618b838f8ec2.avif?t=1771494782\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras_big/e95ec2dfd6c5a253c6bf618b838f8ec2.avif?t=1771494782 width=800 height=91 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>☕ 经营与扩展咖啡厅</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟拉米一起经营咖啡厅，在咖啡厅内来回穿梭，运用不同的家具与设备，快速完成客人点单！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras/233c22a31564f3f1b9f789b6700c0241.poster.avif?t=1771494782\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras/233c22a31564f3f1b9f789b6700c0241.webm?t=1771494782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras/233c22a31564f3f1b9f789b6700c0241.mp4?t=1771494782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏡 自由设计你的咖啡厅</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打造属于你的梦想咖啡厅！摆放家具、装饰，一切由你决定。不同的摆设还会影响咖啡厅的效果！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras/6e46e1c7d1fc89613d6f8288a5dbf188.poster.avif?t=1771494782\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras/6e46e1c7d1fc89613d6f8288a5dbf188.webm?t=1771494782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras/6e46e1c7d1fc89613d6f8288a5dbf188.mp4?t=1771494782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⌨️程式节奏游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验爆肝程式人的日常，随着音乐节奏进行挑战，完成开发任务！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras/1e57e682e8f2eb60d33b2a0862c25967.poster.avif?t=1771494782\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras/1e57e682e8f2eb60d33b2a0862c25967.webm?t=1771494782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras/1e57e682e8f2eb60d33b2a0862c25967.mp4?t=1771494782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🔧 工坊制作 &amp; 升级拉米</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透过工坊制作各种道具，打造新的家具、升级设备，甚至可以强化拉米的能力，让她能帮助你更有效率地经营咖啡厅！解锁更多可能性，让你的店铺更加独一无二！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras/bd67968101464c7fb616cb2adf288711.poster.avif?t=1771494782\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras/bd67968101464c7fb616cb2adf288711.webm?t=1771494782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras/bd67968101464c7fb616cb2adf288711.mp4?t=1771494782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras/b2913794c0eafdcf072b3e34d08943a5.poster.avif?t=1771494782\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras/b2913794c0eafdcf072b3e34d08943a5.webm?t=1771494782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196150/extras/b2913794c0eafdcf072b3e34d08943a5.mp4?t=1771494782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>準備好迎接挑戰了嗎？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>《拉米：程式與咖啡》</strong>中，你將面對經營挑戰、技術升級，以及探索爺爺留下的秘密。這個咖啡廳裡，隱藏著更多不為人知的故事，等待你與拉米一同揭開。</p>",
